{
  "stem": "8703.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Us, the majority of the people from [INAUDIBLE], we were put into cattle cars, closed in, and they were taking us away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were there in the cattle cars, locked in, without food, without water, for five days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Every once in a while, they handed-- they-- they gave-- they threw in some bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I couldn't eat without water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I found out that it's more important-- water is more important than food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you can live without food, even, for a few days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But without water, it was very, very, extremely hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My lips were black and I felt so badly, and I got sick.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't feel well because I didn't have any water and I couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My brother felt much better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after-- there were-- there were-- over there, it was terrible in the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were about 75 or 80 people with a pail of our necessities, you know, to relieve ourselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one-- especially one very fine, intelligent person-- some people got sick, mentally sick in-- and in this because--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were men and women at this point, or just men?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Women was over there, too--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In different-- in different cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for some reason, the women over there were in front, and the-- and the cattle cars in the back never got any-- any-- any water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once I had a bad experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We gave one-- it-- it-- he was a Russian or a Ukraine-- we paid him $100, he should bring us a bottle of water.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took the $100-- it was 100 zloty-- and he took the [INAUDIBLE] and he threw away just the bottle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then we tried again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to do something.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
